            "text": "Jeremiah 5:3",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and submit their necks to the yoke, which laid the foundation of all their rebellion. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Truth is perished, and is off from their mouth; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " there is no trusting or believing them in any thing they say or do; no veracity or fidelity, but perfidious both to God and men, being all filed with hypocrisy, lies, and deceits. ",
        "children": []
